<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section xml:id="Grading">

  <title>Grading</title>
  
   <subsection>
      <title>Homework</title>

      <p>
        Homework for this course will be submitted through the online system MyOpenMath.  
        To create an account and enroll in our course, go to <url href="https://www.myopenmath.com/" visual="myopenmath">MyOpenMath</url> and either 
        log in using your existing account, or create a new account by clicking on 
        `Register as a new student.'  Use the following information to find our course:
        <dl>
            <li>
              <title>Course Name:</title>

              <p>S26 Introduction to Functions</p>
            </li>

            <li>
              <title>Course ID:</title>

              <p>315120</p>
            </li>

           <li>
            <title>Enrollment Key:</title>
            
            <p>s26math</p>
          </li>
        </dl>
        Homework assignments can be worked on past the due date by using a ``Late Pass.''  
        Work done under a Late Pass will receive a minor grade deduction.  
        All homework assignments, even those done using a Late Pass, must be completed by the last day of classes.
      </p>
    

    </subsection>

    <subsection>
    <title>Quizzes/Classwork/Assignments/Projects</title>

      <p>
        No makeup assignments here, but I will drop your lowest two quiz scores.  
      </p>
    </subsection>


   <subsection>
    <title>Exams</title>
        <p>
          We will have three in-semester exams held on the following dates.
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p>
                Monday, February 23rd
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                Monday, March 30th
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                Monday, April 27th
              </p>
            </li>
            
          </ul>
        </p>
  </subsection>

  <subsection>
    <title>Final Exam</title>

      <p>
        Our cumulative final exam will be held Monday, May 11th from 8:00am-11:00am in Hemenway Hall 405.
      </p>
    </subsection>




    <subsection>
      <title>Final Grades</title>

      <p>
        The following percentage weights are used for calculating your weighted course average.
      </p>
    
      <tabular halign="right">
        <row header="yes" bottom="minor" >
          <cell>Category</cell>
          <cell>Weight</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
